Enum Class Extension

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Extension>
org.gbif.api.vocabulary.Extension
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Extension>, Constable
public enum Extension extends Enum<Extension>
Enumeration of dwc extensions for both Occurrence and Taxon that are indexed by GBIF.
